# CLI Binaries Directory

Place compiled WardnMesh CLI binaries here before building the desktop app.

Expected files:
- wardn (macOS/Linux)
- wardn.exe (Windows)

Build commands:
```bash
# Using Bun (recommended)
bun build src/cli.ts --compile --target=bun-darwin-arm64 --outfile=wardn-darwin-arm64
bun build src/cli.ts --compile --target=bun-darwin-x64 --outfile=wardn-darwin-x64
bun build src/cli.ts --compile --target=bun-linux-x64 --outfile=wardn-linux-x64
bun build src/cli.ts --compile --target=bun-windows-x64 --outfile=wardn-windows-x64.exe
```

These binaries will be bundled with the desktop app and installed by the setup wizard.
